title: blinding smite
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

The next time you hit a creature with a weapon attack before this spell ends (up to 1 minute later), your weapon flares with bright light, and the attack deals extra [[radiant damage|damage type]] to the target. Additionally, the target must resist your magic or be blinded for up to a minute.